    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Through several questionaries the investigators will measure the satisfaction of patients
      diagnosed with anaphylaxis in the use of a medical device for the adrenaline autoinjector, a
      smart case for an epinephrine autoinjector connected via Bluetooth to a mobile application.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
